msg: Thank you for participating in this charity auction!
You have single-handedly helped a community in
Ethiopia get one step closer to clean water.
We teamed up with the 21ADA stake pool and
Run For Water charity to do tangible good with the
opportunities you guys have given us. We hope that
you all continue to support our mission and invest in
our us! In turn, we promise to never leave this space
and continue to make cool art for you all.
- The Rokindo Collective
